    "description": "Super Arter/《超级阿特》是一款受到《马里奥对抗大金刚》启发的解谜/平台游戏，重点是拾取钥匙解谜开门。采用16位游戏启发的像素艺术。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090550/extras/07c65da20dba5d4b609f27fd01b53e70.poster.avif?t=1751897732\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090550/extras/07c65da20dba5d4b609f27fd01b53e70.webm?t=1751897732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>跳跃，投掷物品，使用开关，躲避陷阱，击败敌人等等，克服你路径上的障碍，同时寻找开启下一关门的钥匙，解救通往每个世界的首领，收集所有多米诺遗物。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在多达5个不同的世界中解决各种难题，包含多个关卡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090550/extras/347e129f2150ed1b65f6bd0851be0ec0.poster.avif?t=1751897732\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090550/extras/347e129f2150ed1b65f6bd0851be0ec0.webm?t=1751897732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>每个世界结束时要面对强大的首领</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090550/extras/d68873590d4cac2dd93a567381f0c614.poster.avif?t=1751897732\" width=620 height=68 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090550/extras/d68873590d4cac2dd93a567381f0c614.webm?t=1751897732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>寻回被黑暗巫师偷走的多米诺遗物，解决最具挑战性的谜题，面对敌人，收集礼物，并发现阿特拿到开门的钥匙的最佳方式，体验这款独特的平台/解谜游戏。",
